{"type":null,"faqId":49787,"title":"华为智能手表_如何使用日历？","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body10349436\"><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329167__p57357275191459\">在配对的手机日历应用中新建活动并设定时间段，设置成功后一段时间会自动同步到手表上，手表会在既定时间内会发出提醒。</p><div class=\"note\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329167__note46453433191459\"><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/7c50b_fut2z.gif\"><span class=\"notetitle\"> 说明： </span><div class=\"notebody\"><ul id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329167__ul15427719191459\"><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329167__li4631751191459\">您可以在手表上查看当天的日程。</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329167__li41685760191459\">手表发出日程提醒后，您可以左滑日程通知卡片选择暂停提醒、在手机上打开或屏蔽该应用。</li></ul></div></div></div><div><div class=\"familylinks\"></div></div></body>","faqTypeId":721,"faqType":"软件与APP使用","useful":1,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022329167","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Software-Apps","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1448605855000,"seriesProductName":"Mercury-G00,Mercury-G01,Mercury-G10","visitedTimes":54,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"日历","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}